N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 5303.8 - Processing

State Regulations

The commission shall process only complete applications. The processing of any application shall not constitute any agreement or
acceptance by the commission that the requirements of article 13 of the Racing, Pari-Mutuel Wagering and Breeding Law and Parts 5303 through 5307 of this Title
have been satisfied. Notes
